{"tid":597690,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係唔明點解連登仔成日叫人唔好表白","createTime":"2018-03-19T00:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T05:09:54.000Z","uid":35324,"like":50,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9aedc2f6aadfd7b9069d3e78591835748161b9a9","tid":597690,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T00:56:13.000Z","msg":"叫人一野拖落去實冇死，表白就驚尷尬，衰咗會冇朋友做喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n作為一個絲打，我都試過比人直接用行動表白<br />\n嗰日出出下街，個男仔突然間搭住我膊頭，將我拉埋去佢個身度，攬到勁實<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老尾我嗰下真係呆撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻掙扎想fing甩佢隻手<br />\n點知佢唔肯鬆手<br />\n再過多十幾秒佢先放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢一鬆手之後我即刻走人<br />\n無啦啦比佢攬實真係勁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走佬到返屋企途中我都一直喺度諗 呢個男仔到底係唔係精神有問題 我真心以為佢癲撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好心你地啲連登仔啦，成撚日以為自己好吸引，一野拖住條女就成功<br />\n事實上你諗得表唔表白，即係你唔知條女鍾唔鍾意你啦<br />\n如果佢咁啱鍾意你，咁你拖咪成功囉<br />\n如果佢唔鍾意你嘅，你咁樣強行同人有身體接觸，人地當你係抽水嘅痴線佬咋，之後更加冇friend做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n何況表白呢樣野有咩唔好？<br />\n大家正正經經確立一段關係，怕怕醜醜咁講真心話<br />\n成功之後肯定會成為最美好嘅回憶<br />\n就算失敗，點都好過條女當你痴線驚撚咗你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登仔咪再亂咁叫人直接拖女仔手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0437ef542c55e9821531d43b36edefad3de38e90","tid":597690,"uid":61398,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:02:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d8aa3dd83a2dc9b2473355133828960b1ec782d","tid":597690,"uid":127032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0437ef542c55e9821531d43b36edefad3de38e90","tid":597690,"uid":61398,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:02:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddd1adebb095c7909705c851dcb0b5b54b20e15","tid":597690,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:06:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8baf7937ba2f406119e1b066d9f30105f3405cdf","tid":597690,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0437ef542c55e9821531d43b36edefad3de38e90","tid":597690,"uid":61398,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:02:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:06:29.000Z","msg":"我真心以為佢癲撚咗"},{"pid":"cdc95e776cdccd153223ec38bc1290a0bf83024f","tid":597690,"uid":107927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:06:50.000Z","msg":"旗仔很長"},{"pid":"c772d20863f3aa1d8bd03706f7d34089ed68bb9a","tid":597690,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:07:37.000Z","msg":"唔好轉移話題 你班on9連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30d8ec5a4a9b35fa6815d1674966e2bba1c8a61","tid":597690,"uid":61398,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:11:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63ced3e24f49bb3b597cd3d8ac41c5e66cce5041","tid":597690,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:25:52.000Z","msg":"冷靜D照下鏡,睇下自己個樣, 同埋睇下你本銀行存摺有幾多錢先啦   世界好公平   如果人人都心想事成  會天下大亂  世上總要有你D咁既廢人"},{"pid":"6c9b39262b16c737a71430935c396aab345cf3ea","tid":597690,"uid":7081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a30d8ec5a4a9b35fa6815d1674966e2bba1c8a61","tid":597690,"